SSL certificate |

Provides encryption to webiste , api , db etc 


Ingress controller performs ssl/tls termination 

ğŸ”¹ What SSL/TLS termination means

Decrypting encrypted HTTPS traffic at a trusted point

It:

Terminates the encrypted connection

Converts traffic to plain HTTP internally

ğŸ“Œ This is safe inside a private cluster network



Node Selector  is for environment isolation
---------------

NodeSelector in simple words 

NodeSelector lets you choose which nodes a pod can run on, based on node labels.

Nodes can be labeled with environments like env=dev, env=test, env=prod.

Pods use NodeSelector to specify which labeled nodes they are allowed to run on.

This ensures pods start only on the nodes of the correct environment.

ğŸ”¹ Example

Node labels:

kubectl label nodes node1 env=prod
kubectl label nodes node2 env=dev



